{"tid":729483,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有線中國組：三星深圳廠方遷往東南亞、蘇州外商投資斷崖式暴跌","createTime":"2018-07-04T14:53:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-09T07:05:57.000Z","uid":79563,"like":31,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"9b532d91729eb48a4bbcd88b0b3f5d1ba3eec0ab","tid":729483,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T14:53:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/cablechinadesk/videos/1704270243050788/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fcablechinadesk%2Fvideos%2F1704270243050788%2F&d=ZcOiAZcDZ2f5NvGWbb8lmJ4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=cf79cd21\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/cablechinadesk/videos/1704270243050788/</a><br />\n<br />\n【三星深圳廠方遷往東南亞】<br />\n【蘇州外商投資斷崖式暴跌】<br />\n<br />\n三星在深圳的通訊設備生產廠房，月初開始已逐步辭退三百多名員工，到現在已停止運作。好像三星這樣外資企業廠房關閉，是否個別事件呢?<br />\n<br />\n一直以外資企業主導的蘇州，自2013年外資企業的工業投資創出1200億歷史高峰後，就逐年下降，到去年已累積跌了30%，至今年一、二月份，蘇州總體的工業投資，就只剩下99億元🇨🇳人民幣🇨🇳，跌幅比去年同期超過了五成。這些數據跟過去幾年多間大型外資企業從蘇州撤離中國，相當吻合。<br />\n<br />\n至於蘇州和深圳相似的地方，就是過去五年工業投資佔比下降期間，地產投資就逐年上升。"},{"pid":"9c9ae9f58aee9a0aa3417aea087ad4fd96a247be","tid":729483,"uid":17859,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T14:54:04.000Z","msg":"八九六四當年外資撤離 +x入市 賺到隻閪咁<br />\n今年大灣區+x撤離 廢中廢老快啲入市變下個+x <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10db980164429c9cd4f0ecd1c6cca61d57760313","tid":729483,"uid":79563,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"9c9ae9f58aee9a0aa3417aea087ad4fd96a247be","tid":729483,"uid":17859,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T14:54:04.000Z","msg":"八九六四當年外資撤離 +x入市 賺到隻閪咁<br />\n今年大灣區+x撤離 廢中廢老快啲入市變下個+x <img src=\